lines.text: You two for a nickel, jive time, freak time whore.
Let me tell you niggas one thing. Zito or Biggs or nobody shits on my head! Now you niggas got that?

And then they killed Rochelle. Shot her in the fuckin' head. But chicks like your bullshit, bourgeois daughter can do anything they want to do. Because you got the bread to make it cool. Ain't that right, Oliver? But the Rochelle's of the world coming from the streets, man, end up dead, or hustlin' or hookin'. Let me tell you one thing, man. That shit has got to stop.
Alright man you done got what you want outta me. You gonna let me go?
You're the way I like my men - proud and erect.
Run, Uncle Remus. Run, fat greasy nigga!
You're not leaving again, Tyrone. What am I supposed to do, sit here with my finger?
